dct_title_s: Map of New Jersey : compiled from the latest authorities
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. "Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1856 by Charles Desilver ... " Includes table of distances of "Routes from Trenton" and table of population statistics for "Counties and county towns of New Jersey." At upper right: 13. From: New universal atlas ... Philadelphia : S. Augustus Mitchell, 1856.
